Major issue being translating doc or the query or both or using bilingual
Why using dismax aprser
To cater phrasequeries on languages :
For instance, we found out that boosting the native language relevant documents gives better result
sine transliteration of documents are not full proof

EDISMAX query parser provides parameters pf, pf2 and pf3 to boost the document based on certain criteria.
We utilize this feature to provide extra boost to documents in favour of native language
